  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="3970718200">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-3970718200" class="vote-count">0</span>
              <a id="btn-3970718200" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="3970718200">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/72722453/">CC</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3970718200">2023-10-23 02:38:35</a>
          <span class="comment-location">浙江</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">主线剧情依然精彩，魂器的概念也很抓人眼球。但是感情戏写得一塌糊涂。毫不惹人注意的金妮突然变成了大美女，魁地奇天才，魔咒天才，纯纯为了男主变成了标签工具人。对金妮的厌恶更是在为了维护哈利怒怼从头到尾都是理智的赫敏时抵达了巅峰。不会写感情戏可以不写，不换是哈金还是罗赫敏，都一塌糊涂一言难尽！</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1432596/?comment_id=3970718200"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="3966360576">
